list.item:
Use of cyclobenzaprine hydrochloride extended-release capsules for periods longer than two or three weeks is not recommended [

                           see Indications and Usage (1)

                        ].

text.paragraph:
The use of cyclobenzaprine hydrochloride extended-release is not recommended in patients with mild, moderate, or severe hepatic impairment [

                              see Warnings and Precautions (5.4

                           ) and Clinical Pharmacology (12.3)].
